HIGH PROTEIN - Protein contributes to the maintenance of muscle mass.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R24_W15_UK_QR18089-5_Main_low-4931eb1e.jpg
